  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42948</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_023_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>精霊晶核って、精霊さんの卵なんだよね？
あれから精霊さんが生まれるの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You said that an Atomism Core is the Spirit's egg, right? Is that where they are born from?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43048</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_023_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>簡単に言えばそうなるが、
そんな簡単な話でもない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You could say it's that simple that but at the same time it's much more complicated.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43112</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_023_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>…………？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43212</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_023_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>精霊晶核そのものだけでは、
精霊は生まれないのさ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Just with an Atomism Core a Summon Spirit can't be born.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43348</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_023_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そっか、そんな簡単に精霊さんが生まれたら、
世界中精霊さんまみれになっちゃうもんね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's right, if the Summon Spirits were born that easily then the world would be filled with them!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43472</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_023_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>凝縮したマナのエネルギーを与えてやって
初めて精霊晶核に精霊の命が宿る</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>With the massive amount of Mana energy the egg holds, the Spirit's life itself dwells inside.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43580</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_023_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>が、そのエネルギーというのが
そう簡単には手に入らない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But getting your hands on that energy could be really hard...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43720</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_023_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そっか、つまりそれはヒヨコが生まれる卵と
そうでない卵があるのとおんなじってことなんだね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I see... a small bird that was born from an egg that isn't really an egg. It's kinda like that, uh!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43852</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_023_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ニワトリ……まぁ、端的に言うとそうだが……
精霊晶核がいっきに安っぽくなるな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>A chicken...? It's really hard to explain but... Atomism Core is unlike anything else...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43924</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_023_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>フライパン、ない？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Got any Fry pans?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43996</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_023_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>食うんじゃないぞ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Don't even think about it...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
